snippet.title: USA: Anarchists and police clash during May Day protest in Seattle, 9 arrested

localized.description:
Police gave a heavy-handed response to an anarchist May Day protest march in Seattle, Sunday. The demonstrators were marching under the banner, "Whoever they vote for, we are ungovernable."
